      "updated": 1780657321
    },
    {
      "id": "6a22af0500000000003b1271",
      "text": "井戸端だと[hoagecko.icon]さんがアクティブユーザ？",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1780657926,
      "updated": 1780657955
    },
    {
      "id": "6a22af1100000000003b1272",
      "text": " 使い心地はどんな感じか気になる[zatsma.icon]",
